  "texts": [
    "**badges**: This table lists the badges awarded to users.",
    "Each badge has a unique ID, and the table records the user ID of the recipient, the badge name, and the date it was awarded. 4.",
    "**posts**: This table contains detailed information about each post, including post ID, post type ID, accepted answer ID, creation date, score, view count, body text, owner user ID, last activity date, ti-tle, tags, answer count, comment count, favorite count, last editor user ID, last edit date, community owned date, parent post ID, closed date, owner display name, and last editor display name.",
    "The table provides a comprehensive overview of the content and interaction metrics for each post. 5.",
    "**users**: This table stores information about users, including user ID, reputation, account creation date, display name, last access date, website URL, location, selfintroduction, views, upvotes, downvotes, account ID, age, and profile image URL."
